{"title":"打铁的来了","authors":["杨恰"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":12,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"打铁的来了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杨恰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叮叮噹，叮叮噹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打铁的下了乡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风箱忽达忽达响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫得社员心里忙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社员王老汉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要打张大铁锨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“哥们多辛苦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给咱们锻一锻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明儿去挖河泥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使着利索点。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打铁的咧嘴乐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大手一忽闪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“哥们放心吧！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用不着嘱咐咱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱到这儿来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也是为支援生产。”"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}